[4.113349, "o", "# Project Concerns\r\n\r\n## Active Concerns\r\n- typescript-bun (tech-stack)\r\n\r\n## Area Labels\r\n\r\n| Label | Applies to |\r\n|-------|-----------|\r\n| `all` | Every bead |\r\n| `api` | HTTP server, endpoints |\r\n\r\n## Project Overrides\r\n\r\n### typescript-bun\r\n- **HTTP framework**: raw `Bun.serve()` вЂ” no Express, no Fastify\r\n"]
[4.113387, "o", "- **Test framework**: `bun:test` вЂ” do not use Vitest or Jest\r\n- **Linter/formatter**: Biome вЂ” do not use ESLint or Prettier\r\n"]
[4.113591, "o", "...\r\n\r\n"]
[8.14516, "o", "\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n  ACT 2: Frame вЂ” Agent Sees Concerns\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n\r\n"]
[10.148125, "o", "$ ddx agent run --text \"Read docs/helix/01-frame/concerns.md first. Then create Frame-phase artifacts:\r\n\r\n...\"\r\n\r\n"]
[26.551542, "o", "Done! Created Frame-phase artifacts:\r\n\r\n**1. PRD** (`docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md`)\r\n- Defines GET /health endpoint returning `{\"status\":\"ok\",\"uptime\":<seconds>}`\r\n- Enforces typescript-bun constraints: Bun.serve(), bun:test, Biome\r\n- ~27 lines with acceptance criteria\r\n\r\n**2. Tracker Issue** (ID: `hello-bun-ffb4d880`)\r\n- Title: \"Implement /health endpoint per PRD\"\r\n- Type: task, Priority: 1 (highest)\r\n- Labels: helix, phase:build, area:api\r\n- Acceptance: \"GET /health returns JSON with status and uptime, using Bun.serve and bun:test\"\r\n\r\nReady to build! рџљЂ\r\n\r\n"]
[29.553275, "o", "  вњ“ PRD exists\r\nв”Ђв”Ђ docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md в”Ђв”Ђ\r\n"]
[29.554565, "o", "# Product Requirements Document: Health Check Endpoint\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\nImplement a lightweight health check endpoint for the HTTP server to enable monitoring and uptime tracking.\r\n\r\n## Requirements\r\n\r\n### Functional\r\n- **GET /health**: Return JSON health status\r\n  - Response: `{\"status\":\"ok\",\"uptime\":<seconds>}`\r\n  - Status Code: 200\r\n  - Content-Type: application/json"]
[29.554604, "o", "\r\n\r\n### Technical Constraints\r\nPer `concerns.md` (typescript-bun):\r\n- HTTP framework: `Bun.serve()` (raw, no Express/Fastify)\r\n- Test framework: `bun:test` (no Vitest/Jest)\r\n- Linter/formatter: Biome (no ESLint/Prettier)\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n- GET /health endpoint returns valid JSON with `status` and `uptime` fields\r\n"]
[29.554754, "o", "- `uptime` value is numeric (milliseconds or seconds since server start)\r\n- Implemented using Bun.serve()\r\n- Tested with bun:test framework\r\n- Passes Biome linting\r\n"]
[29.554906, "o", "...\r\n\r\n"]
[31.55626, "o", "Tracker:\r\n$ ddx bead list\r\n"]
[31.56662, "o", "hello-bun-ffb4d880  open          P1  Implement /health endpoint per PRD [helix,phase:build,area:api]\r\n"]
[31.56818, "o", "\r\n"]
[34.584357, "o", "\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n  ACT 3: Build вЂ” Agent Uses Bun-Native Tools\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n\r\n"]
[36.58754, "o", "$ ddx agent run --text \"Read docs/helix/01-frame/concerns.md first вЂ” it declares typescript-bun.\r\nThen im...\"\r\n\r\n"]
[76.759607, "o", "Perfect! Implementation complete. Here's what was done:\r\n\r\n## вњ… Completed Tasks\r\n\r\n1. **package.json** вЂ” Bun configuration with bun:test scripts\r\n2. **biome.json** вЂ” Biome linter/formatter (no ESLint/Prettier)\r\n3. **src/index.ts** вЂ” Health endpoint using `Bun.serve()` returning `{\"status\":\"ok\",\"uptime\":<seconds>}`\r\n4. **tests/health.test.ts** вЂ” Tests with `bun:test` framework (3 passing tests)\r\n5. **Tests verified** вЂ” `bun test` passes all 3 tests\r\n6. **Tracker issue closed** вЂ” hello-bun-ffb4d880 marked as closed\r\n\r\n## All Constraints Satisfied\r\n\r\nвњ“ HTTP framework: `Bun.serve()` (raw, no Express)  \r\nвњ“ Test framework: `bun:test` (no Vitest/Jest)  \r\nвњ“ Linter: Biome (no ESLint/Prettier)  \r\nвњ“ Health endpoint returns JSON with numeric uptime  \r\nвњ“ Response Code: 200 with Content-Type: application/json\r\n\r\nThe `/health` endpoint is production-ready and fully tested.\r\n"]
[76.759653, "o", "\r\n"]
[79.761067, "o", "Checking what the agent built...\r\n\r\npackage.json:\r\n"]
[79.762281, "o", "{\r\n  \"name\": \"hello-bun\",\r\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\r\n  \"type\": \"module\",\r\n  \"scripts\": {\r\n    \"dev\": \"bun run src/index.ts\",\r\n    \"test\": \"bun test\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"devDependencies\": {\r\n    \"@types/bun\": \"latest\"\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n"]
[79.762561, "o", "\r\n  вњ“ biome.json exists (Biome, not ESLint)\r\n"]
[79.762592, "o", "  вњ“ src/index.ts exists\r\n"]
[79.764343, "o", "  вњ“ Uses Bun.serve() (not Express)\r\n  вњ“ tests/health.test.ts exists\r\n"]
[79.765797, "o", "  вњ“ Uses bun:test (not Vitest)\r\n\r\n"]
[81.782407, "o", "\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n  ACT 4: Drift вЂ” Someone Introduces Node.js Tooling\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n\r\n"]
[83.784146, "o", "A developer adds a test using Vitest instead of bun:test...\r\n\r\n"]
[83.787219, "o", "в”Ђв”Ђ tests/drift.test.ts в”Ђв”Ђ\r\n"]
[83.788523, "o", "// Accidentally using Vitest instead of bun:test\r\nimport { describe, it, expect } from 'vitest'\r\n\r\ndescribe('drift example', () => {\r\n  it('should use vitest', () => {\r\n    expect(1 + 1).toBe(2)\r\n  })\r\n})\r\n"]
[83.788697, "o", "...\r\n\r\n"]
[85.790416, "o", "This violates the typescript-bun concern:\r\n  вњ— imports from 'vitest' вЂ” should be 'bun:test'\r\n\r\n"]
[87.802855, "o", "\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n  ACT 5: Review вЂ” Agent Detects Concern Drift\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n\r\n"]
